main event: A round, spinning object was sighted near the North Star over Oahu, Hawaii by a Marine at the Kaneohe Naval Air Station.
interesting points: The object changed colors, appearing red, white, blue, and green.
The object appeared to be spinning.
The object was about 45 degrees above the horizon and very bright.
There was another black object that appeared to be with the spinning object.
The sighting lasted for over an hour.
sighted object: A round, spinning object with a black object nearby
witnesses: Marine at Kaneohe Naval Air Station
